OL,5,MPlants in Space!
OL,7,GPlants in Space! Our first email to
OL,8,Gattendees about EMF will be going out
OL,9,Gsoon, but in the meantime, we’d like
OL,10,Gto announce the Greenhouse early, to
OL,11,Ggive folks a chance to get their
OL,12,Gplants ready! What is The Greenhouse?
OL,13,GBuilding on the success of 2024, the
OL,14,Gplant exchange is back - with a new
OL,15,Gname! Plant Sharing You are invited to
OL,16,Gonce again bring small cuttings,
OL,17,Goffshoots, seedlings, bulbs or spare
OL,18,Gseeds for everyone to browse and
OL,19,Gselect from to take home. There will
OL,20,Gbe trays for keeping your plant
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
